<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Domain Not Connected - Curated.cx</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 3rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #1a202c;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: #4a5568;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .hostname {
        font-family: monospace;
        background: #f7fafc;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        color: #2d3748;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .help-text {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #718096;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Domain Not Connected</h1>
      <p>
        The domain <span class="hostname"><%= @hostname %></span> is not currently connected to any site.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're the owner of this domain, please check your domain settings or contact support.
      </p>
      <div class="help-text">
        <p>This domain needs to be configured in the Curated.cx admin panel before it can be used.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
